imdb.plot outline: "Animal Alliance" is a Webshow series hosted by Ellen Lavinthal. The series highlights various issues and happenings that relate to animals ranging from puppy mils to animal friendly politicians, a protest against the dolphin slaughters in Taiji and the campaign to ban fur in West Hollywood and much more.
imdb.title: Animal Alliance
